Titolo: Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Army Men: Soldiers of Misfortune is a third-person shooter video game developed by Big Blue Bubble and published by Zoo Games for Wii, Nintendo DS and PlayStation 2, becoming a Nintendo exclusive in Europe. It is the latest home console game in the Army Men series and the only one to be released on seventh-generation platforms. It is a major departure from prior games in the series in that players assume the role of a child who plays with toy soldiers instead of the toy soldiers themselves, shrinking down to their size to participate in a war among them.

Genere: Third-person shooter

Valutazione: 35
